column2: an A.M. Eatery////My plate was presentable and a good portion. The hashbrowns were yummy (I always add cholula) and the ranchero sauce was decent
column3: but sadly my poached eggs were cold. This really took away from my enjoyment of the plate. Cold eggs make me feel sad - whomp whomp. Â We got our food in good time
column4: so not sure how they cooled so fast. Regardless
column5: ask me...did I finish my plate? Yes...yes I did.
